  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK166">
<l>koṭuppa taḻukkaṟuppāṉ cuṟṟa muṭuppatūu </l>
<l>muṇpatūu miṉṟik keṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who is envious at a gift (made to another) will with his relations utterly perish destitute of food and rainment.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
